name: Cannavigator.com
description: The CNV coin is a crypto currency designed to be used in the Cannavigator Platform and with Cannavigator Payments. The total amount of CNV coins available for purchase is 420,000,000 Coins. Cannavigator Coin will invest 20% of its total market cap to developing Products, investments will be deducted from the capital available in the form of a loan. CNV Coin provides a digital infrastructure that drives research, innovation, development, education, trade, and investments in the Cannabis Industry.
